moji\" /> ）入黎突擊檢查<br />\n跟住話要擇低我個名然後話俾訓導知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁我就驚死（驚要見家長<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n為左唔想搞大件事咁只能先發制人<br />\n於是就即刻拉佢去後樓梯<br />\n拉開褲褳放條巨龍入佢個口到<br />\n逼佢含到雪雪聲<br />\n然後佢喊住咁話唔好唔好<br />\n仲話最多下次扮睇唔到<br />\n但我諗起佢平時佢捉人個時好有威嚴<br />\n仲惡過啲女miss<br />\n之前又捉過我幾次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n心入面嘅怒火變得更大<br />\n咁我就即刻禁低佢<br />\n除左佢條底褲<br />\n將我條佢龍插入佢個已經濕潤咗嘅小穴<br />\n瘋狂插到我feel到佢隻腳軟軟地<br />\n而最後我都頂唔順<br />\n一野射哂落佢塊臉到<br />\n佢見我冇哂力於是就著番衫走<br />\n係佢勒番好皮帶個陣<br />\n我係佢耳邊講話下次唔好再咁<br />\n唔係下次就唔會係插你幾次咁簡單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢塊面紅紅地低頭話嗯ok<br />\n最後我就放左佢走<br />\n從此以後次次係班房食野都冇皇管<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40886dff2150741b371cc5d2726caaaeb5d0e9a2","tid":834853,"uid":199378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T13:06:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1b9e5f068b306187d5ee3e1d0aa138f36a8aa005","tid":834853,"uid":138732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"40886dff2150741b371cc5d2726caaaeb5d0e9a2","tid":834853,"uid":199378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T13:06:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T13:25:35.000Z","msg":"係 食咗好多低from囡囡<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ca4d07978425228cee8cc208fd1ec2e87bf9247","tid":834853,"uid":27797,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T13:28:10.000Z","msg":"中學生涯未屌過perfect 先係人生點遺憾<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb3a355df8fe8d2f1f64fcd1f2c476ec464d6cc3","tid":834853,"uid":27797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T13:29:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中學生涯未屌過perfect 先係人生遺憾<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"